1> download the GOTM-dev (not GOTM-4.0) from http://www.gotm.net/index.php?go=software
2> modify the path of GOTM_BASE in configure.sh
3> modify the path of CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX in configure.sh
4> run configure.sh
5> find the paths of folders 'include' and 'lib' 
6> set the paths of GOTMLIB and GOTMINCS accordingly
